(8, 4, '2015-08-08 09:40:31', '2015-08-08 09:40:31', 'Omega goes beyond monitoring. We focus upon thoroughÂ assessments, comprehensiveÂ investigations, full disclosure and effective remediation. We strive to ensure that all parties, from manufacturers, trading entities, logistics providers, brands and retailers have full transparency over their supply chain partners, product and associates. We enable our clients to understand any shortcomings then provide them with the expertise to remediate effectively allowing them to operate their supply chains with complete confidence.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2017-02-28 21:26:21', '2017-03-01 05:26:21', '', 0, 'http://local.omega.com/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
