(120, 4, '2015-09-07 19:59:02', '2015-09-08 03:59:02', '<div class="ethicsLogoContainer">\r\nEstablished Partnership With<br /><a href="https://secure.ethicspoint.com/domain/en/report_custom.asp?clientid=16944" target="_blank"><img src="https://local.omega.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/logo_ethics.png" alt="logo_ethics" width="263" height="55" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-28" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>ETHICS</h1>\r\n<p class="highlight">At Omega, we practice what we preach. A stringent internal Code of Ethics requires our staff to uphold exceptional levels of integrity, honesty and transparency at all times.</p>\r\n<p>To ensure that our standards are never compromised, Omega has an established partnership with <a href="https://secure.ethicspoint.com/domain/en/report_custom.asp?clientid=16944" target="_blank"><span class="colorHighlight">EthicsPoint<sup>Â®</sup></span></a> to provide a multilingual, anonymous and confidential method for all employees and business partners to report any concerns or misconduct.</p>\r\n<p>Please take some time to review our Code of Ethics. If you are unclear about an issue or wish to voice a concern please do <strong><a href="../contact/">contact us</a></strong>. The information you provide will be sent to us by <a href="https://secure.ethicspoint.com/domain/en/report_custom.asp?clientid=16944" target="_blank"><span class="colorHighlight">EthicsPoint<sup>Â®</sup></span></a> on a totally confidential and anonymous basis.</p>\r\n<p>Our commitment to integrity sets us apart.</p>\r\n<a href="https://secure.ethicspoint.com/domain/media/en/gui/16944/Omega_Code_of_Ethics_1_22_07.pdf" target="_blank" class="btnFileReport"><span>Review Our Code Of Ethics</span></a><br /><br />\r\n<a href="https://secure.ethicspoint.com/domain/en/report_custom.asp?clientid=16944" target="_blank" class="btnFileReport"><span>File a Report</span></a>\r\n', 'Ethics', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-07 19:59:02', '2015-09-08 03:59:02', '', 12, 'https://local.omega.com/12-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
