 by a preventative, collaborative approach with pressure from all levels. Omega has vast, practical experience in this field. Should you be interested to learn more about our services please do contact us.', 'Auditor Bribery Is A Complex Issue and Requires Careful Management at All Levels', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '224-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-10 22:13:32', '2015-12-11 06:13:32', '', 224, 'https://local.omega.com/224-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
