y questions you should be asking.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '246-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-14 23:44:58', '2016-01-15 07:44:58', '', 246, 'https://local.omega.com/246-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
