 business, please contact us.', 'How Do I Prevent Bribery Across My Supply Base?', 'Consumer brands and retailers have clear protocols governing unethical supply chain practices within their own organizations.Â  However, very few have equivalent procedures for managing cases of bribery involving external partners.  This is a major blind spot. ', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '254-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-28 00:51:24', '2016-01-28 08:51:24', '', 254, 'https://local.omega.com/254-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
